<section id="requirements" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
                           xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                           xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
  <title>Requirements</title>
  <para>
    To create your own ITE toolkit and remote control extensions, you
    need:
  </para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        <emphasis role="strong">GUI</emphasis><emphasis>dancer</emphasis>
        7.0 / Jubula 2.0 or later
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Eclipse 3.4 or later (4.2 recommended)
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        JDK 5.0
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Full write access in installation directory for deploying the
        extension.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>